Le Creuset Screwpull Lever and Foil Cutter Gift Set
List.Description:
This Lever and Foil Cutter set from Le Creuset is simply outstanding. This lever is a 21st century redesign of the original Hebert Allen lever corkscrew invented in 1980 and offers unrivalled performance, experience, and rigorous testing. This corkscrew removes synthetic and natural corks with ease. It has a hand sharpened stainless steel screw, with 3 coats of extra strong nonstick coating, and a comfortable and stable grip, even on flanged bottles. Matching foil cutter has 4 wheels. Box included for storing lever and foil cutter when not in-use.



Gift Set Includes:
  • Le Creuset Lever
  • Le Creuset Foil Cutter
  • Le Creuset Gift Box
